        custom_tooltip = {
            text = sunni_creation_independent
            hidden_tooltip = {
                in_revolt = no

                    independent = yes

                        any_liege = {
                            OR = {
                                in_revolt = yes

                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        OR = {
            trait = mirza

        }

            AND = {
                trait = sayyid
                piety = 1000
            }
            custom_tooltip = {
                text = controls_mecca_medina
                hidden_tooltip = {
                    719 = {
                        owner = {
                            OR = {
                                is_liege_or_above = ROOT
                                character = ROOT
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    718 = {
                        owner = {
                            OR = {
                                is_liege_or_above = ROOT
